---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="KCode Pro" description="Unlock advanced AI coding features with KCode Pro: swarm mode, RAG indexing, analytics, and more.">
  <section class="hero container">
    <h1>KCode Pro</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
      Advanced features for professional developers. Supercharge your workflow with
      multi-agent orchestration, intelligent indexing, and deep analytics.
    </p>
    <div class="ctas">
      <a href="https://kulvex.ai/checkout" class="btn btn-primary">Start Pro &mdash; $19/mo</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <h2>Pro Features</h2>

    <div class="pricing-grid">
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <h3>Multi-Agent Swarm</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 0.5rem;">
          Spawn parallel sub-agents to divide and conquer complex tasks.
          Each agent works in its own context, coordinating through message passing.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pricing-card">
        <h3>Codebase RAG Indexing</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 0.5rem;">
          Automatically index your codebase for semantic search.
          The AI finds relevant code faster without you having to point it to files.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pricing-card">
        <h3>Advanced Analytics</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 0.5rem;">
          Detailed breakdowns of token usage, tool frequency, cost tracking,
          and session performance metrics.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pricing-card">
        <h3>Adaptive Effort</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 0.5rem;">
          Ensemble cost-awareness that automatically adjusts model effort levels
          based on task complexity, saving tokens on simple queries.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pricing-card">
        <h3>Auto-Pin Context</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 0.5rem;">
          Intelligently detects and pins the most relevant files to your conversation
          context so the AI always has the right code in view.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pricing-card">
        <h3>Priority Support</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 0.5rem;">
          Get help faster. Pro users receive priority responses on GitHub issues
          and access to a dedicated support channel.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <h2>Activate Pro</h2>
    <div class="install-options">
      <div>
        <h3>1. Purchase a license</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);">
          Subscribe at <a href="https://kulvex.ai/checkout">kulvex.ai/checkout</a> to receive your Pro key.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3>2. Activate in KCode</h3>
        <pre><code>kcode pro activate YOUR_PRO_KEY</code></pre>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted);">Your key is stored locally and never sent to third parties.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <h2>FAQ</h2>
    <div class="faq">
      <details>
        <summary>Can I try Pro features before buying?</summary>
        <p>Yes. Run <code>kcode pro trial</code> to activate a 14-day free trial with full access to all Pro features.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Does Pro require an internet connection?</summary>
        <p>Only for license validation (once per session). All Pro features work fully offline with local models after validation.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Can I use Pro with my own API keys?</summary>
        <p>Absolutely. Pro enhances KCode's capabilities regardless of which LLM provider you use. Bring your own Anthropic, OpenAI, or any other API key.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>What happens if I cancel?</summary>
        <p>KCode reverts to the free tier. All your data, sessions, and configurations remain intact. You can resubscribe anytime.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Is there a team discount?</summary>
        <p>Yes. The Team plan at $49/seat/month includes centralized management. For larger deployments, contact us for Enterprise pricing.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
